# VLAN-TRUNK
 VLAN-MULTI SWITCH TRUNK
A VLAN trunk link was established between the two switches to carry multiple VLANs across the connection. Both switches were configured with the same VLAN IDs (VLAN 2 and VLAN 3) to ensure seamless VLAN traffic forwarding and proper inter-switch communication for the connected devices.

# SWITCH CLI-COMMANDS
**1.SWITCH TO SWITCH**

Switch (config)#int fa 0/5

Switch (config - if)# switchport mode access

Switch (config - if# switchport mode trunk

**2.VLAN CLI COMMAND**

Switch (config# int fa 0/1

Switch(config-if)# switchport mode access

Switch(config-if)# switchport access van 2

**(SAME FOR VLAN COMMAND ALL DEVICES)**
